      • ParsingContext

        public new(forceVisibility : boolean,
           isTestingPhase : boolean)
        Constructor with specific visibility configuration.
        Parameters:
        forceVisibility - forces all the elements to be visible. The visiblilty tags such as SarlDocumentationParser.Tag.ON and SarlDocumentationParser.Tag.OFF will have no effect if the value of this argument is true.
        isTestingPhase - indicates if the context is created for testing phase.
